    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Fred w. Heslewood, national or\nganizer of the Industrial Workers\nof the World, was arrested in Occur\ndAlene yesterday on a charge of\ncriminal conspiracy in connection\nwith the local free speech fight.\n\n\nHeslewood is fighting extradition.\nHe was taken into custody by Cap\ntain of Detectives M. J. Burns.\nChief of Police Sullivan and Prose\ncutting Attorney Pugh were present.\nThe officers held a requisltlon from\nGovernor Hay calling on the Idaho\nauthorities to deliver up the pris-\nOner.\n\n\nHeslewood is being held in Occur\nd'Alene pending the return of the\nextradition papers from Governor\nBrady of Idaho."
    }
  ]
